      <title>边缘政党收获后，德国的债务制动器改革有疑问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/german-fringe-parties-strong-showing-clouds-path-to-debt-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国面临着更宽大的财政政策的有限途径，周日议会选举威胁要减少下一步政府的选择，试图将经济摆脱漫长的停滞之阵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/german-fringe-parties-strong-showing-clouds-path-to-debt-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 05:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Olam以期待已久的交易将农业企业股份出售给沙特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-23/olam-group-confirms-sale-of-agri-business-stake-to-saudi-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡的Olam Group Ltd.达成了一项期待已久的交易，以销售其农业企业单位的控制权，该单位交易大块谷物，并制造从可食用的油到意大利面，再到沙特阿拉伯的国有食品贸易公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-23/olam-group-confirms-sale-of-agri-business-stake-to-saudi-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2025 22:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
